#▗▄▄▞▘▗▞▘▝▚▖▐▌ ▐▌▐▌ ▐▌▐▙▄▄▀▐▌ ▐▌▝▚▄▄▖

# Open Terminal
super + {_,shift + }Return
	{alacritty, bspc node -s biggest.local}

# Quit BSPWM
super + shift r
	bspc wm -r
# Restarts sxhkd
super + shift s
	pkill -USR1 -x sxhkd
# Quit BSPWM
super + shift q
	bspc quit

# Call rofi menus
super + {d, x, p, b, f, w}
    {$HOME/.config/bspwm/rofi/scripts/launcher.sh, $HOME/.config/bspwm/rofi/scripts/powermenu.sh, $HOME/.config/bspwm/rofi/scripts/wallpaper.sh, $HOME/.config/bspwm/rofi/scripts/bluetooth.sh, rofi -show filebrowser -theme /home/skilax/.config/bspwm/rofi/menu.rasi, rofi -show window -theme /home/skilax/.config/bspwm/rofi/menu.rasi }

#  #  #  #  #  KEYS

# Volume Controls
XF86AudioRaiseVolume
    /home/skilax/.config/bspwm/bin/volume.sh --up
XF86AudioLowerVolume
    /home/skilax/.config/bspwm/bin/volume.sh --down
XF86AudioMute
    /home/skilax/.config/bspwm/bin/volume.sh --toggle
# Brightness Controls
XF86MonBrightness{Up,Down}
	/home/skilax/.config/bspwm/bin/brightness.sh {--up, --down}
#XF86MonBrightness{Up,Down}
#  brightnessctl s 10{+,-}%

#Caps_Lock
super + space
	~/.config/bspwm/bin/layout.sh
# screenshot
Print
	flameshot gui
shift + Print
	flameshot full



#  #  #  #  #  BSPWM


#Kill window
super + c
	bspc node -{c}

# set the window state
super + Up
	bspc node -t fullscreen
super + Down
	bspc node -t tiled

# Switch workspace
#super + {Left,Right}
#	bspc desktop -f {prev,next}.local

# focus or send to the given desktop
super + {_,shift + }{1-9,0}
	bspc {desktop -f,node -d} '^{1-9,10}'

# Change focus to next window, including floating window
alt + {_,shift + }Tab
    bspc node -f {next.local,prev.local}

# Reboot
super + ctrl + r
        reboot

# Power Off
super + ctrl + p
        poweroff

# alternate between the tiled and floating layout
super + t
	bspc node -t "~"{floating, tiled}
# Choose direction to open window
super + alt + {Left,Down,Up,Right}
	bspc node -p {west,south,north,east}

# Cancel direction to open window
super + alt + space
	bspc node -p cancel

# Launch Applications
super + shift + {f,n,t}
	{flatpak run org.mozilla.firefox, \
	nemo, \
	telegram-desktop}
